{"tid":1440360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴警在大圍放催淚彈　有長者不適","createTime":"2019-08-10T11:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:02:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf066d090b2939044072f53458aaa844a5ef462b","tid":1440360,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"大批原本在大埔的示威者，傍晚轉往大圍、沙田及紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n部分示威者在大圍美田路迴旋處設置路障，防暴警察不久後到場，並快速推進，施放多枚催淚彈驅散示威者。有長者懷疑吸入催淚氣體不適，需要途人協助離開。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察其後跑上天橋，要求在天橋上的市民離開。"},{"pid":"ca2855f1b865e6abd9637ba62cd7761f3b61e597","tid":1440360,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=4e3db226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣就係做比藍絲、港豬<br />\n做比自己人睇有撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fd49dadcddf48ad7b958ef1082fbda6a6cbb10","tid":1440360,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427910f8928816845837b15e63f465806